snippet.title: Quintus and the Formidable Curse | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2440100/Quintus_and_the_Formidable_Curse/

The teaser trailer for the upcoming video game 'Quintus and the Formidable Curse'. The game will be a direct sequal to the video game 'Quintus and the Absent Truth', which was released on PC and all last and current gen consoles.

Official Website: https://www.wrecktangles.com/qatfc
